               <p>WILLIAM SPRIGGINS. I live in Skinner-street, and <rs id="t18260914-437-viclabel2464" type="occupation">have an umbrella-shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-437-victim2269 t18260914-437-viclabel2464"></join> in <placeName id="t18260914-437-crimeloc2465">Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-437-crimeloc2465" type="placeName" value="Fleet-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-437-crimeloc2465" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-437-off2462 t18260914-437-crimeloc2465"></join>. My son came to me about half-past nine o'clock on the morning of the 14th of August, and told me that an umbrella had been taken.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182609140165"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-437-person2270">
                  WILLIAM 
                  STAPLETON
               <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2270" type="surname" value="STAPLETON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2270" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2270" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a journeyman carpenter. On the 14th of August I was in Fleet-street, and heard the cry of Stop thief! - I saw the prisoner running as fast as he could; I pursued, and took him in Poppin's-court, with the umbrella.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-437-person2271">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SPRIGGENS
               <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2271" type="surname" value="SPRIGGENS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2271" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2271" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's son. I saw the prisoner come in and take the umbrella off the rail, and run off with - he was brought back by the witness.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-437-person2272">
                  DANIEL 
                  TURNER
               <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2272" type="surname" value="TURNER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2272" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-437-person2272" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the officer, and took the prisoner.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had been two days without food, and the officer, seeing my distressed situation, gave me something to eat.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18260914-437-verdict2466" type="verdictDescription">
